## 8. PROVIDER-UTILS: KEY FUNCTIONS FOR IMAGE MODELS

### API Call Functions

**postJsonToApi** - for JSON requests:
```typescript
export const postJsonToApi = async <T>({
  url: string;
  headers?: Record<string, string | undefined>;
  body: unknown;
  failedResponseHandler: ResponseHandler<APICallError>;
  successfulResponseHandler: ResponseHandler<T>;
  abortSignal?: AbortSignal;
  fetch?: FetchFunction;
}): Promise<{ value: T; responseHeaders: Record<string, string> }>;
```

**postFormDataToApi** - for multipart form data (image editing):
```typescript
export const postFormDataToApi = async <T>({
  url: string;
  headers?: Record<string, string | undefined>;
  formData: FormData;
  failedResponseHandler: ResponseHandler<APICallError>;
  successfulResponseHandler: ResponseHandler<T>;
  abortSignal?: AbortSignal;
  fetch?: FetchFunction;
}): Promise<{ value: T; responseHeaders: Record<string, string> }>;
```

### Response Handlers

**createJsonResponseHandler** - parses JSON responses:
```typescript
export const createJsonResponseHandler = <T>(
  responseSchema: FlexibleSchema<T>,
): ResponseHandler<T>;
// Returns: Promise<{ value: T; responseHeaders: Record<string, string> }>
```

### Utility Functions

**combineHeaders** - merges header objects:
```typescript
export function combineHeaders(
  ...headers: Array<Record<string, string | undefined> | undefined>
): Record<string, string | undefined>;
```

**convertToFormData** - converts objects to FormData:
```typescript
export function convertToFormData<T extends Record<string, unknown>>(
  input: T,
  options?: { useArrayBrackets?: boolean },
): FormData;
```

**Base64 Utilities:**
```typescript
export function convertBase64ToUint8Array(base64String: string): Uint8Array;
export function convertUint8ArrayToBase64(array: Uint8Array): string;
export function convertToBase64(value: string | Uint8Array): string;
```

**Other Essential Functions:**
```typescript
export function loadApiKey({
  apiKey: string | undefined;
  environmentVariableName: string;
  description: string;
}): string;

export function loadOptionalSetting({
  settingValue: unknown;
  environmentVariableName: string;
}): string | undefined;

